{"tid":161089,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"代餐減肥 你問我答","createTime":"2017-03-18T09:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T15:11:53.000Z","uid":64200,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f166ab1edd20f3baa6a703f3fbfdde46f28758fe","tid":161089,"uid":64200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:41:53.000Z","msg":"樓主小學時最高峰去過230磅，yr 1時185磅，唔想做毒撚，經做傳銷（直銷？）嘅組媽介紹食代餐，用咗1年減到140磅，宜家final year 上返150磅（176cm)<br />\n<br />\n真人真事，非打手，勿討論牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110c4efd20221a765426238f8981116c7a970340","tid":161089,"uid":8516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:43:06.000Z","msg":"冇做運動？"},{"pid":"e6e96181192a3055806dc9e34b24542d092e42ce","tid":161089,"uid":64200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:44:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇做運動？</blockquote><br />\n有 1星期3日 每次慢跑30分鐘（怕傷膝）"},{"pid":"6d52d2beef5e1c4e3cff89dae58d242f50449b1d","tid":161089,"uid":70292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:14:07.000Z","msg":"簡單講係食藥物減肥？"},{"pid":"f9c054dc49fb5b9ca4afa279fca5c5391c51adff","tid":161089,"uid":64200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T13:44:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>簡單講係食藥物減肥？</blockquote><br />\n代餐唔係藥物"},{"pid":"0dbe6eb08a6f0a90fc819444743323a68335e927","tid":161089,"uid":32583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"herberlife<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191d8a73a35a4c52637b09ef0945252bc33feb3b","tid":161089,"uid":32583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T13:46:59.000Z","msg":"Btw 真係有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c40627023ab14ae49ca069c7bb307c6e3945e0","tid":161089,"uid":5667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:29:34.000Z","msg":"有冇餐單參考下"},{"pid":"225af17cb97e6a2561a0a1be3d35001f2ac26906","tid":161089,"uid":35702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:33:05.000Z","msg":"重點係做運動唔關代餐事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21f99e50a3c0e695c88a1453c35f794b77333a4","tid":161089,"uid":32583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:37:23.000Z","msg":"原理大約係 早餐代餐 吸收大約200卡路里<br />\n午餐食正餐 1000卡路里<br />\n晚餐代餐 200卡路里<br />\n而代里係低卡路里得黎又有營養<br />\n而成年人每日大約要吸收2500左右<br />\n中間那個差距就係你身體到拿走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e018ad895de9a30dfd5e4c31cf138b68bb22789b","tid":161089,"uid":64200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇餐單參考下</blockquote><br />\n餐單冇特定，都係canteen頹飯多，屋企煮盡量㨂菜食 每餐7成飽 每日代一餐"},{"pid":"613cc81b8c14245fc21bf75d0fbdefde3494edee","tid":161089,"uid":64200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:40:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重點係做運動唔關代餐事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想效果快啲梗係配合做運動<br />\n唔做運動，只要計好熱量，長遠都係會瘦，不過慢好多"},{"pid":"9085454ad450a3d18d18a242d1e5f1a735b236ab","tid":161089,"uid":64200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>重點係做運動唔關代餐事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想效果快啲梗係配合做運動<br />\n唔做運動，只要計好熱量，長遠都係會瘦，不過慢好多</blockquote><br />\n不過我有時就算計好熱量，營養都係唔均衡，特別係限1800kcal嗰時, 蛋白質好多時都不足70g"},{"pid":"17e681435b04f0c73a6a3e54c43d1e48b3e30ef8","tid":161089,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T15:11:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>簡單講係食藥物減肥？</blockquote><br />\n代餐唔係藥物</blockquote><br />\n食物入面有藥？"}]}